OL,3,C'Patients are dying in corridors': NHS
OL,4,Cworker reveals hospital chaos
OL,6,FITV News Health Correspondent Rebecca
OL,7,FBarry investigates the rise in
OL,8,Fhospital corridor care
OL,10,FAn NHS whistleblower has told ITV News
OL,11,Fthat patients are "dying in corridors"
OL,12,Fbecause of a lack of available
OL,13,Fhospital beds.
OL,15,FOur investigation into so-called
OL,16,Fcorridor care in NHS hospitals has
OL,17,Fexposed "chaotic" conditions for
OL,18,Fpatients and staff, not confined to
OL,19,Fthe traditionally busy winter months.
