OL,3,C'Patients are dying in corridors': NHS
OL,4,Cworker reveals hospital chaos
OL,6,FLast summer, there were almost 5,000
OL,7,Fdeaths associated with long A&E waits,
OL,8,Faccording to analysis by the Royal
OL,9,FCollege of Emergency Medicine, shared
OL,10,Fexclusively with ITV News.
OL,12,FAn A&E worker spoke anonymously to ITV
OL,13,FNews.
OL,15,F"Today I walked through A&E and there
OL,16,Fwere patients upon patients on oxygen
OL,17,Fin the corridors," he said.
OL,19,F"It's embarrassing to work for the
OL,20,FNHS. It's heartbreaking, it's
OL,21,Fdepressing."
