OL,6,F"It was horrendous. We were in tears
OL,7,Fmost of the time."
OL,9,FIf you or a family member has been
OL,10,Faffected by this story, you can email
OL,11,Fus at healthstories@itv.com
OL,13,FBernard is partially sighted and can't
OL,14,Fwalk without help. Staff left food
OL,15,Fnext to him - but he couldn't see it.
OL,17,F"He didn't know where he was when he
OL,18,Fwas on that corridor. He was just
OL,19,Ftalking to the wall because he
OL,20,Fcouldn't see," Sharron said.
