OL,6,F"He ended up with severe burns from
OL,7,Flying in his own urine."
OL,9,FThe backlog in hospitals is, in part,
OL,10,Fcaused by delayed discharges -
OL,11,Fpatients who are medically fit to
OL,12,Fleave, but can't, often because of a
OL,13,Flack of social care.
OL,15,FAnalysis by the Royal College of
OL,16,FEmergency Medicine (RCEM) shared
OL,17,Fexclusively with ITV News suggests:
OL,19,FThe President of the Royal College of
OL,20,FEmergency Medicine, Dr Ian Higginson,
OL,21,Fdescribed the findings as "appalling".
