OL,3,C'Patients are dying in corridors': NHS
OL,4,Cworker reveals hospital chaos
OL,6,F"There is absolutely rock-solid
OL,7,Fevidence that long waits in the
OL,8,Femergency departments are associated
OL,9,Fwith an increased risk of dying - and
OL,10,Fthat's what really worries us," Dr
OL,11,FHigginson said.
OL,13,F"The last two shifts I've worked in my
OL,14,Femergency department, I've had very
OL,15,Fsenior nurses in tears at the state of
OL,16,Fwhat's going on - and at times I feel
OL,17,Flike crying too.
