OL,6,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "The care Mr
OL,8,FParkinson received was completely
OL,9,Funacceptable and should not happen.
OL,11,F"While there have been clear
OL,12,Fimprovements this winter ` with faster
OL,13,Fambulance handovers, shorter delays
OL,14,Fand fewer hospital beds occupied by
OL,15,Fflu patients ` it is deeply concerning
OL,16,Fthat some people are still being
OL,17,Ftreated in corridors. It is
OL,18,Fundignified, and the government is
OL,19,Fdetermined to fix the mess it
OL,20,Finherited.
